    "type": "message",
    "text": "<@UJN1TAYEQ> maybe the term villifies it a bit, but it's a real problem with SC and tidal IMO :wink: You evaluate statements like\n\n\n    a = SomeInstrumentDefinition()\n    a.play()\n\n...and when you delete those lines you can no longer do `a.stop()`. It's even worse when you don't even store the \"thing\" in a variable but just .play() it right away",
